social_posts.post_text: Weekend Recap: celebrated  @mackinnonm being the most beautiful bride I have ever seen, got to have my best girls with me in my favorite place and finally met Pete the parrot. 🤍🥹

As a pet owner, I know that hair comes with the territory and I’m used to having a lint roller handy but wouldn’t it be nice to just throw on a clean outfit and not worry about it?! #ad Thanks to the @maytag Pet Pro System from @loweshomeimprovement, we may have finally found the answer! 

The @maytag Pet Pro System Washer (which removes up to 5x the pet hair) and Dryer are a match made in heaven! The washer includes a Pet Pro Filter made to specifically reduce pet hair from your laundry. Couple that with the XL lint trap in the dryer and you may just be able to grab that favorite black shirt more regularly. 

Head to @loweshomeimprovement to check out this one of a kind system for yourself!! Our house is very excited about it! 

Disclaimer: *Comparing normal cycle with Pet Pro filter and option to cycle using traditional agitator without Pet Pro filter and option. Results will vary based on fabric and type of pet hair.

#lowes #founditatlowes #lowesxmaytagpetpro #maytag #maytagpets

Christmas, a new year, family, friends, dogs, beach trips, curling, busted pipes, hikes, confetti + many undocumented happy moments in-between.

My precious creatures. 🥹🤍 

Thank you for these, @lauramollphoto. I will cherish them forever.

ADOPT NINA (or share her please)!!!!! This extra, extra, extra special girl has been waiting far too long for her forever home. Nina is an 8 year old mixed breed pup looking for her retirement home. Nina is as sweet and mellow as they come, she’s just looking for a soft, gentle place to call home! She is good with dogs, kids and will make the perfect companion for truly anyone but especially someone with a soft spot for an older dog that they can spoil rotten and give this girl the life she has always deserved. Please share Nina with your senior dog lovers, she deserves the absolute best! @wagsandwalksnashville

Let our dogs pick the perfect day to celebrate National Pet Day with our friends at @vetericyn. Their happiness, health and care is a daily priority and we love pampering them with Vetericyn's FoamCare Shampoo, especially after a day with all of their favorite things! #NationalPetDayVetericynWay #Vetericyn #VetericynPartner #NationalPetDay

Spent the morning looking back on the last 10 years of our life (today is our 6 year wedding anniversary + we met 10 years ago) and I’m emotional now, so I’m just going to keep this caption short. Happy Anniversary, @dansmyers. Growing up with you has been the absolute joy of my life. Can’t wait for all of the years to come. I love you so much. It’s you + me. 🤍
It was a 10/10 week. 💕 If you are in need of a laugh, check out the last slide for how we knew mama deer had returned 😳🤣 (@dansmyers, the dogs and 🦌 are all fine, so laugh away).

I am so excited to be partnering with the International Fund for Animal Welfare, also known as IFAW, to help encourage all of us to be better prepared for our pets in the case of a natural disaster. 

Living in Nashville and growing up in Kansas, I’m far too familiar with tornadoes but the reality is none of us are immune and we must be prepared to protect our sweet animal friends! To take your first steps in preparedness, head to the link in my bio to learn more about IFAW and get your Free Disaster Ready Starter kit! 

@ifawglobal
#DisasterReady #SaveAnimalLives #BeReady #IFAW #GetThereInTime #NaturalDisasters #sponsored
A few weeks back. 🩵🌊
Shelter days are my favorite days. 🩵

I love this dog so much. Meet Honey, a recent @wagsandwalksnashville rescue that has stolen all of our hearts. First and foremost I want to say Honey WILL be ok. Her condition, while very painful and tough to see, is treatable and she will improve each and every day. I am saying this more gently than my heart feels, Honey was failed. This could have been prevented and please, if you have a dog, take care of them. Treat them with the love and dignity they deserve. You are all they have. Honey never had to know this pain and that’s what brings me to tears but I’m so grateful for incredible rescues and fosters stepping in and taking on these responsibilities. To support Honey’s ongoing care in her healing journey, please find links in my story as well as on @wagsandwalksnashville’s page. 🩵
Summer. 🩵☀️🌼🐸

My heart could explode typing this: The @wagsandwalksnashville Adoption Center is officially opening this weekend + we got to share a little sneak peek last week with some very special donors, sponsors and friends! I am absolutely beaming with pride over what @kathrynhurley_ and the incredible Wags team have accomplished and the impact that this special place will have on our community. Thank you to everyone who has believed in this mission and this space. We are going to save all the dogs!!!! 🩵🐶 (Dan + I are so proud to have sponsored a part of the center and have our sweet creatures honored where so many pups will meet their forever families.)
Welcome to the good life, babies. 🩵

Daniel!!!! It’s your birthday!!!! I love you more than the giant smile plastered on my face every minute that I’m with you. Always gonna be by your side, through every hair evolution, forever + ever. 😂🩵 Wish this wonderful man a happy birthday, y’all!!!
Wags babies. 🩵🥹 (ft. Lunchbox, Petal, Chip ✨adopted today✨, Brady, Snackpack, Matilda + Ollie ✨adopted today✨)

Adopt Rabbit!!! The man with the best ears, the best smile and now just needs to find a best friend! Check out @wagsandwalksnashville for more info on this buddy!!! 🩵 #adoptdontshop #adoptable

Bigger Houses is OUT NOW!!! This is my favorite @danandshay record hands down. I am so proud of how hard these guys have worked to create this album but also how hard they have worked (and continue to work) on themselves as a duo and as individuals. I love you both very much and @dansmyers, you are absolutely one of kind. I feel so lucky to walk alongside you. I love you unconditionally. Listen to Bigger Houses right now + then again + again + again.
Then again…it always would have been you.

Very grateful for you, my crew. 🧡Happy Thanksgiving to all!

There are 6 hours left of Giving Tuesday and if you are feeling called to support an organization this holiday season, I cannot think of a more worthwhile cause than @wagsandwalksnashville. The community impact and lives saved is hard to put into words but if you need a number, 118 dogs have been saved in the month of November alone. Animal rescue has changed my life, given me purpose and I’m honored to be part of this incredible team. 🩵 Link to donate in my bio + stories.
A sweet end to a sweet year. Wishing everyone a Happy New Year! ❤️
